title: Ebro In The Morning - DaBaby Baby Drama + Rosenberg's Crazy Cab Ride
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 11/16.

Ebro's obsession with the new Silk Sonic album continues, the Flashing Lights reports shine light on the DaBaby's baby drama, and Rosenberg tells us about his crazy cab ride (56). 

Hot 97 is helping New York City Teachers.
